                    <head>No. 8.<lb/><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Baker</persName> to
                            Mr. <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi></head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Managua</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-03-06"><hi rend="italic">March 6,
                            1894</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                    <p>Consul Braida telegraphs fifty English soldiers landed Bluefields; strongly
